didn't work on me. didn't work.

360
00:23:49.054 --> 00:23:51.366
- He's gonna be…
- yes. it did. I saw you jump.

361
00:23:51.390 --> 00:23:52.534
You did.

362
00:23:52.558 --> 00:23:55.203
Come on. buddy. Come on. pal.

363
00:23:55.227 --> 00:23:56.955
